{
  "stem": "8916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I ended up on Schindler's list and in Schindler's company, working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When-- when he was-- then when we were in the ghetto and my father had a job outside of the ghetto, as so many did, it was a great advantage to be able to leave the ghetto to go to work and then come back.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because that way we had a chance to contact non-Jewish people on the outside and able to organize and get some additional food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it was an advantage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father would-- used to bring stuff stuffed in his pockets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, we had the exchange, because in the same-- in the factory where he worked as a Jew, there were other working people who were non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was a certain amount of contact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in that way, it was an advantage to have a job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she had a job in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a cleaning lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was cleaning barracks and offices.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was a hardworking lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She could-- it was not hard for her to do this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had a-- she had a hard life all along, you know, taking care of  four children, five children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Between-- between-- between the two of them and what we could do as children to earn something, we were able to survive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody did something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody did something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a natural thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A normal thing to do was to bring it home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother would then use it to put food on the table.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I must mention this, that at the time that we were in the ghetto, we were only-- there were only four children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The oldest one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Hershel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he didn't stay around for the Germans to overtake him.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
